# Group Misc

Miscellanous resources.

## Live counters [/live-counters]

### Get live counters [GET]

Return the current number of players (total / online) and servers (total / active).

::: note
#### Server-side caching

This resource has a cache lifetime of **1 minute**.
:::

+ Request

    + Headers

            Authorization: Token {token}

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Attributes (Map Counters Object, fixed-type)

+ Response 403 (application/json)

    Invalid token or token not provided.

    + Attributes (Error Response, fixed-type)

+ Response 503 (application/json)

    Maintenance in progress.

    + Attributes (Error Response, fixed-type)